    </p>

    <h2>
        <div><img src="/assets/img/openkeychain.svg"></div>
        OpenKeychain
    </h2>
    <p>
        <a href="https://www.openkeychain.org/">OpenKeychain</a> for Android
        uses <span class="brand">keys.openpgp.org</span> by default
